5. Risk Management

Material Degradation: Mitigated by high-performance bio-resins and specialized UV-topcoats.
Print Delamination: Addressed through controlled heated-chamber printing and continuous monitoring of extrusion temperature.
Regulatory Hurdles: Proactive collaboration with maritime safety bureaus to set new standards for 3D-printed bio-vessels.



6. Budget & Investment

The project will be funded through a combination of:
Hennepnatie Coop Shares: Direct community investment.
Sustainability Grants: EU Green Deal and Innovation funds for circular economy projects.
Early-Adopter Pre-orders: High-net-worth individuals seeking sustainable luxury.
